1. sudo apt-get update

2. sudo apt-get install vsftpd

3. sudo gedit /etc/vsftpd.conf

Make sure about the following:
anonymous_enable=YES
local_enable=YES
write_enable=YES

4. sudo service vsftpd restart

5.
HOST:
ifconfig (for get IP)
ls
sudo gedit abc
ls
ls

client:
ftp 192.168.0.109(HOST IP)
HOST NAME
HOST PASS
get abc(abc=File name HOST)
put abb(abb=File name of Client)
